Privacy Policy for Bible Verses for Every Situation App

Effective Date: 1/10/2024

This privacy policy explains how the Bible Verses for Every Situation app handles your data. The app respects your privacy and is designed to protect your personal information. Please read this policy carefully to understand how your information is managed.

1. No Data Collection

The Bible Verses for Every Situation app does not collect, store, or process any personal data. The app operates offline and does not require an internet connection to function. Therefore, no personal information such as your name, email address, or location is collected or shared.

2. Notification Permissions

The app may request permission to send push notifications. This permission is used solely to deliver daily Bible verse notifications. These notifications are managed on your device and do not involve any data transmission to us or third-party services. You can manage or disable notifications at any time in your device settings.

3. No Third-Party Services

The app does not integrate with any third-party services, analytics, or advertising platforms. It functions independently without connecting to external servers, APIs, or any form of online services.

4. Permissions

The app may request access to certain device functionalities, such as storage or notifications, to improve your experience. However, these permissions are strictly for app functionality, and no data is transmitted or shared with us or any third party.

5. Security

Even though the app does not collect any data, we are committed to ensuring that your experience is secure. The app does not communicate with external systems, reducing potential security risks.

6. Childrenâ€™s Privacy

The Bible Verses for Every Situation app is suitable for users of all ages, including children. Since no data is collected, the app is compliant with privacy protection laws for children.

7. Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected in this document, and the effective date will be updated accordingly. Please review this policy periodically to stay informed.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

sacredspacewiththelord@gmail.com

By using the Bible Verses for Every Situation app, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

